+## Enabling the endpoint
+
+Set `gateway.http.endpoints.chatCompletions.enabled` to `true`:
+
+```json5
+{
+  gateway: {
+    http: {
+      endpoints: {
+        chatCompletions: { enabled: true }
+      }
+    }
+  }
+}
+```
